sequenceDiagram
    participant Monitor
    participant Nginx
    participant API
    participant DB
    participant Redis
    participant Celery

    loop Every 30s
        Monitor->>Nginx: GET /nginx_status
        Nginx-->>Monitor: 200 OK

        Monitor->>API: GET /api/v1/health
        API->>DB: SELECT 1
        DB-->>API: OK
        API->>Redis: PING
        Redis-->>API: PONG
        API-->>Monitor: 200 OK

        Monitor->>Celery: celery inspect ping
        Celery-->>Monitor: pong
    end

    alt Service Down
        Monitor->>Monitor: Log Alert
        Monitor->>Monitor: Restart Container
    end